text: I'm not sure I have the version with emoji's ... but with other apps I've used I like the emoji's. :slightly_smiling_face: They are fun and are faster to find vs. reading text. Can understand at a quick glance.

You’ll know if you have the emoji’s if it looks like my screenshot above when you’re in the design manager or any other screen a developer is likely to go (it’s currently only in the beta build of the extension - because if the titles aren’t done right some people could get really annoyed lol)

Also you have to have the “UI Tweaks/Dev Menu” toggle on as well

Let’s get Spooky! :ghost:
I’ve gone through our issues and labeled ones that might be easy to jump into without having much experience with how the extension works. Feel free to ask questions in Issues. If something interests you but the issue’s message was vague, just ask and it can be clarified. You’re not alone, if you have questions about how the extension works so you can do your thing, just ask. I watch the issues and I am on Slack way too much
